<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards are stipulated in accordance with Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Venue and equipment maintenance fee standards for the Nanhai Theater and the 3rd Exhibition Room are as follows:

┌──────┬──────────┬─────┬──────┐
│Item        │Time                │Stage     │Performance │
│            │                    │Load-in & │& Event     │
│            │                    │Rehearsal │            │
├──────┼─────┬────┼─────┼──────┤
│Nanhai      │Morning   │08:30~  │NT$5,000  │NT$7,000    │
│Theater     │          │12:00   │          │            │
│            ├─────┼────┼─────┼──────┤
│            │Afternoon │13:30~  │NT$5,000  │NT$7,000    │
│            │          │17:00   │          │            │
│            ├─────┼────┼─────┼──────┤
│            │Night     │19:00~  │NT$10,000 │NT$10,000   │
│            │          │22:30   │          │            │
├──────┼─────┴────┼─────┼──────┤
│Piano       │Per time slot       │NT$800    │NT$800      │
├──────┼──────────┼─────┼──────┤
│Choral Stage│Per time slot       │NT$400    │NT$400      │
├──────┼──────────┼─────┼──────┤
│Dance Floor │Per time slot       │NT$400    │NT$400      │
│Mat         │                    │          │            │
├──────┼──────────┼─────┴──────┤
│3rd         │All day             │NT$600                  │
│Exhibition  │                    │                        │
│Room        │                    │                        │
├──────┴──────────┴────────────┤
│Notes:                                                      │
│1.Venue usage includes the use of A/C, lighting and stereo  │
│  equipment.                                                │
│2.For the use of piano, choral stage and dance floor mat,   │
│  the time slots are the same as venue time slots.          │
│3.Users exceeding aforementioned time slots would be charged│
│  an additional NT$2,000 per hour for the venue, NT$20 per  │
│  hour for the piano, and NT$100 per hour for the choral    │
│  stage and the dance floor mat. Less than 1 hour would be  │
│  charged as 1 hour.                                        │
│4.Any sudden request for an additional session would not be │
│  accepted.                                                 │
│5.In order to maintain the quality of the venue for         │
│  sustainable use, venue  users may leave only after an     │
│  inspection by the center's technical staff following the  │
│  end of their performances and, as regulated, shall        │
│  compensate for any damages discovered.                    │
│6.Government agencies, schools, non-profit educational and  │
│  cultural organizations, and NPOs are given 20% discount   │
│  off the venue fees.                                       │
└──────────────────────────────┘

]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The charges stipulated in these Standards shall be examined and adjusted regularly according to the venue and equipment maintenance costs and the consumer price index (CPI).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards shall take effect on the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
